    "body": "Especially the call error handling code used verbose f-string code for what can be done much simpler with `PyErr_Format()`.\r\n\r\nI also noticed that we generated `__Pyx_PyObject_IsTrue()` for empty-dict tests. It was probably just an oversight that they were left out of the special handling in `CoerceToBooleanNode`.",
